snippet.title: Twenty One Pilots - The Contract (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Official video for the new single “The Contract” from the forthcoming album Breach, out September 2025.

Pre-order / Pre-save Breach: https://top.lnk.to/breach
Stream/Download “The Contract”: https://top.lnk.to/thecontract

THE CLANCY TOUR: BREACH 2025
Tickets and info at https://signup.ticketmaster.com/twentyonepilots

SEP 18 - Cincinnati, OH @ TQL Stadium
SEP 20 - Toronto, ON @ Budweiser Stage
SEP 23 - Milwaukee, WI @ American Family Insurance Amphitheater
SEP 24 - Tinley Park, IL @ Credit Union 1 Amphitheatre
SEP 27 - Hershey, PA @ Hersheypark Stadium
SEP 28 - Burgettstown, PA @ The Pavilion at Star Lake
SEP 30 - Hartford, CT @ XFINITY Theatre
OCT 01 - Bangor, ME @ Maine Savings Amphitheater
OCT 04 - Wantagh, NY @ Northwell at Jones Beach Theater
OCT 05 - Bristow, VA @ Jiffy Lube Live
OCT 07 - Virginia Beach, VA @ Veterans United Home Loans Amphitheater
OCT 08 - Charlotte, NC @ PNC Music Pavilion
OCT 10 - West Palm Beach, FL @ iTHINK Financial Amphitheatre
OCT 11 - Tampa, FL @ MIDFLORIDA Credit Union Amphitheatre
OCT 14 - Orange Beach, AL @ The Wharf Amphitheater
OCT 15 - Alpharetta, GA @ Ameris Bank Amphitheatre
OCT 17 - Birmingham, AL @ Coca-Cola Amphitheater
OCT 19 - Rogers, AR @ Walmart AMP
OCT 20 - Dallas, TX @ Dos Equis Pavilion
OCT 23 - Chula Vista, CA @ North Island Credit Union Amphitheatre
OCT 25 - Los Angeles, CA @ BMO Stadium

LYRICS
I check the doors, check the windows, and pull the blinds,
I check the clock, wondering what he’ll pull this time,
I have a feeling that necromancer’s outside,
And I’m just trying to stay quiet.

I don’t sleep much, that's crazy, how’d you know that?
Keep myself up, that's maybe how you know that,
Promises and contracts I used to keep,
I don’t sleep much, that's crazy, how’d you know that?
Keep myself up, that’s maybe how you know that,
My hallucination I used to see.

Wake up and I find out, did a change up,
Wait — Did it change up?
Is it light out yet?
Better find out. Bet,
Imma walk around the edge of the room,
And the bed where I hide my face,
Pace around,
Better try to breathe,
Pace around, Pace around.

(Sleep I found)
I wanna get out there,
But I don’t try,
I wanna get out there,
But I don’t try.

I used to see,
It felt so real,
But now I plead,
Just take the deal,
I promised you,
A contract.

snippet.description:
Life’s too short not to spend it with the person you love. The final season of The Summer I Turned Pretty begins July 16.

It’s the end of her junior year of college, and Belly’s looking forward to another summer in Cousins with her soulmate, Jeremiah. Her future seems set, until some core-shaking events bring her first love Conrad back into her life. Now on the brink of adulthood, Belly finds herself at a crossroads and must decide which brother has her heart. Summer will never be the same…

snippet.title: I Tried the Top 50 Airbnbs in America - Day 2
snippet.description:
hello new mexico!!!
donate here - https://www.stjude.org/50states



Wheel of Doom penalties:
1. Running on fumes - You must drive until the tank says “empty.”
2. Local Legend - You must share a meal with a local from the nearest town before moving on.
3. Route Roulette - You must receive directions from a stranger and follow them word for word.
4. Reverse Card - You must turn around the way you came and find another way to your next Airbnb.
5. Detour - You are not allowed to drive on highways to the next Airbnb.
6. Silent Treatment – No talking between Ryan & Haley for the entire road trip.
7. Airplane Mode - You must get to your next Airbnb without your phones.
8. Locked Out - You are not allowed to sleep in your next Airbnb.
9. The Split - One of you must split up and find another way to your next Airbnb.
10. Red Light, Green Light - Roll a dice — whatever it lands on, you must wait that many hours before hitting the road.
11. Golden Ticket - Congratulations! You have unlocked immunity for 24 hours. It can be activated at any time.

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Enchanted by Nature | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sims™ 4 Enchanted by Nature Expansion Pack* arrives July 10 and is available for pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack


Order now through Aug 21 for the Fairy Garden Digital Content**: the Lofty Leaf Pond, Luminous Mycena Lantern, and Disguised Dwelling Fairy Home.

Indulge your sense of wonder: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack
Live surrounded by nature and embrace a free spirited lifestyle. Who needs beds and plumbing? It's time to get comfy in the great outdoors by meeting your Sims' needs in nature and Foraging for food and collectables. 

There's a charming world to explore, and it has a mystical side. Experience strange Ailments, craft Elixirs, and even become a Fairy! When creating Fairy Sims, you'll choose from a variety of beautiful wings which you can paint freely.

Available July 10 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation®4, and PlayStation®5. Pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack 

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY. http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack

snippet.title: #1 THUNDER at #4 PACERS | NBA FINALS GAME 3 HIGHLIGHTS | June 11, 2025
snippet.description:
The Pacers defeated the Thunder, 116-107 tonight in Indiana. Bennedict Mathurin led the way for the Pacers with 27 points on 9-12 from the field (2-3 from 3) to go along with 4 rebounds and 2 three pointers. For the Thunder, Jalen Williams had a team-high 26 points on 9-18 from the field (1-2 from 3). The Pacers lead the series 2-1

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: I Tried the Top 50 Airbnbs in America
snippet.description:
50 STATES IN 50 DAYS
donate here - https://www.stjude.org/50states



Wheel of Doom penalties:
1. Running on fumes - You must drive until the tank says “empty.”
2. Local Legend - You must share a meal with a local from the nearest town before moving on.
3. Route Roulette - You must receive directions from a stranger and follow them word for word.
4. Reverse Card - You must turn around the way you came and find another way to your next Airbnb.
5. Detour - You are not allowed to drive on highways to the next Airbnb.
6. Silent Treatment – No talking between Ryan & Haley for the entire road trip.
7. Airplane Mode - You must get to your next Airbnb without your phones.
8. Locked Out - You are not allowed to sleep in your next Airbnb.
9. The Split - One of you must split up and find another way to your next Airbnb.
10. Red Light, Green Light - Roll a dice — whatever it lands on, you must wait that many hours before hitting the road.
11. Golden Ticket - Congratulations! You have unlocked immunity for 24 hours. It can be activated at any time.

Tyler Childers' new album, ‘Snipe Hunter’ is available July 25th: https://tchilders.lnk.to/SnipeHunter
Join the Hickman Holler Hunting Club: https://www.hickmanhollerhuntingclub.com/

“Nose On The Grindstone" out now - https://tchilders.lnk.to/NoseOnTheGrindstone 
Tyler Childers' new album, ‘Snipe Hunter’ is available July 25th: https://tchilders.lnk.to/SnipeHunter

Join the Hickman Holler Hunting Club: https://www.hickmanhollerhuntingclub.com/

Follow Tyler Childers:
https://tylerchildersmusic.com
https://www.facebook.com/tylerchildersmusic
https://www.instagram.com/timmytychilders
https://x.com/TTChilders
https://www.tiktok.com/@timmytychildersmusic

Lyrics:
Daddy worked like mule minin’ Pike County coal 
Til he messed up his back and couldn’t work anymore 
He said one of these days you’ll get out of these hills
Keep your nose on the grindstone and outta the pills
See the ways of this world will just bring you to tears
Keep the Lord in your heart and you’ll have nuttin’ to fear
Live the best that you can and don’t lie and don’t steal
Keep your nose on the grindstone and outta the pills
Well daddy I’ve been trying I just can’t catch a break
There’s too much in this world that I can’t seem to shake
But I remember your words, Lord they bring me to chills 
Keep your nose on the grindstone and outta the pills
Now keep in mind that a man’s just as good as his word
And it takes twice as long to build bridges you’ve burnt
And there is hurt you can cause time alone cannot heal
Keep your nose on the grindstone and outta the pills
Well daddy I’ve been trying I just can’t catch a break
There’s too much in this world I can’t seem to shake
But I remember your words, Lord they bring me to chills 
Keep your nose on the grindstone and outta the pills
Keep your nose on the grindstone

snippet.title: VIBRANT VISUALS & CHASE THE SKIES
snippet.description:
Get ready to Chase the Skies with Vibrant Visuals – because both are coming on June 17! 

Vibrant Visuals transforms the Overworld into a pixel-perfect vacation spot! Experience impressive graphic improvements as water reflects, fog drifts, and waterfalls glimmer. Chase the Skies, and its features, will be available for both Minecraft: Java Edition and Minecraft: Bedrock Edition on June 17. Vibrant Visuals will be available for compatible Bedrock Edition devices only on June 17. 

See here for more details: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/chase-the-skies-coming

snippet.title: Protestors take over streets of Downtown San Antonio, speak out against ICE operations
snippet.description:

The protest, dubbed "Take Back the Alamo," is one of many occurring nationwide.

snippet.title: Kehlani - Folded [Official Visualizer]
snippet.description:
Kehlani - Folded
"Folded' out now! 👔🧺
Stream/DL: https://Kehlani.lnk.to/FoldedID

Subscribe for more official content from Kehlani:
https://Atlantic.lnk.to/KehlaniSubscribe

Follow Kehlani
https://www.kehlani.com/
https://facebook.com/Kehlanimusic
https://twitter.com/Kehlani
https://instagram.com/kehlani

Subscribe for the latest official music videos, official audio videos, performances, behind the scenes and more from Kehlani: https://Atlantic.lnk.to/KehlaniSubscribe

The official YouTube channel of Atlantic Records artist Kehlani.

It doesn’t really need an explanation—you know exactly what Kehlani means when she sings. Without sugarcoating or softening a word, the Bay Area-born two-time GRAMMY® Award-nominated multiplatinum songstress will drop a hard truth in one breath and flip a middle finger in the next. She may extend a seductive invitation or an empathetic plea before leaving you in your thoughts and feelings. Either way, she finds a way to consistently relate without filter. With each move, she strengthens this connection to listeners everywhere.  Kehlani’s 2015 breakout mixtape You Should Be Here received a 2016 GRAMMY® Award nod in the category of “Best Urban Contemporary Album.” On its heels, her 2017 full-length debut SweetSexySavage bowed at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 and eventually went gold. Between selling out dates on the SweetSexySavage Tour, the record closed out the year on Pitchfork’s “The 50 Best Albums of 2017” and Rolling Stone’s “20 Best R&B Albums of 2017.” 

Along the way, she contributed to Suicide Squad: The Album and The Fate of the Furious: The Album and guested on Cardi B’s double-platinum “Ring,” Kyle’s platinum “PLAYINWITME,” and Justin Bieber’s “Get Me,” to name a few. By 2020, she picked up three gold solo singles—"You Should Be Here,” “Honey,” and “Distraction,” for which she received her second GRAMMY® nomination for Best R&B performance. In addition, four platinum singles—“Gangsta,” “The Way” [feat. Chance the Rapper], “CRZY,” and “Nights Like This” [feat. Ty Dolla $ign] and streams in the billions. Not to mention, Billboard Women In Music honored her with the “Rule Breaker Award” as she gathered nominations at the Soul Train Awards and the American Music Awards. Plus, she made show-stopping appearances at Voodoo Music + More, Coachella, and beyond. In the aftermath of 2019’s chart-topping While We Wait mixtape, everything changed. She became a mom. As such, parenthood left an indelible imprint on her second full-length, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t. Out May 8th, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t is described by Kehlani as her most mature body of work, featuring songs based on her own real experiences including recently released “Toxic” and “Everybody Business.” In the end, you’ll know exactly what’s on Kehlani’s mind, heart, and soul on It Was Good Until It Wasn’t.

#Kehlani #Folded #OfficialAudio

The official YouTube channel of Atlantic Records artist Kehlani.

It doesn’t really need an explanation—you know exactly what Kehlani means when she sings. Without sugarcoating or softening a word, the Bay Area-born two-time GRAMMY® Award-nominated multiplatinum songstress will drop a hard truth in one breath and flip a middle finger in the next. She may extend a seductive invitation or an empathetic plea before leaving you in your thoughts and feelings. Either way, she finds a way to consistently relate without filter. With each move, she strengthens this connection to listeners everywhere.  Kehlani’s 2015 breakout mixtape You Should Be Here received a 2016 GRAMMY® Award nod in the category of “Best Urban Contemporary Album.” On its heels, her 2017 full-length debut SweetSexySavage bowed at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 and eventually went gold. Between selling out dates on the SweetSexySavage Tour, the record closed out the year on Pitchfork’s “The 50 Best Albums of 2017” and Rolling Stone’s “20 Best R&B Albums of 2017.” 

Along the way, she contributed to Suicide Squad: The Album and The Fate of the Furious: The Album and guested on Cardi B’s double-platinum “Ring,” Kyle’s platinum “PLAYINWITME,” and Justin Bieber’s “Get Me,” to name a few. By 2020, she picked up three gold solo singles—"You Should Be Here,” “Honey,” and “Distraction,” for which she received her second GRAMMY® nomination for Best R&B performance. In addition, four platinum singles—“Gangsta,” “The Way” [feat. Chance the Rapper], “CRZY,” and “Nights Like This” [feat. Ty Dolla $ign] and streams in the billions. Not to mention, Billboard Women In Music honored her with the “Rule Breaker Award” as she gathered nominations at the Soul Train Awards and the American Music Awards. Plus, she made show-stopping appearances at Voodoo Music + More, Coachella, and beyond. In the aftermath of 2019’s chart-topping While We Wait mixtape, everything changed. She became a mom. As such, parenthood left an indelible imprint on her second full-length, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t. Out May 8th, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t is described by Kehlani as her most mature body of work, featuring songs based on her own real experiences including recently released “Toxic” and “Everybody Business.” In the end, you’ll know exactly what’s on Kehlani’s mind, heart, and soul on It Was Good Until It Wasn’t.

#Kehlani #Folded #OfficialAudio

snippet.title: I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets!
snippet.description:
#ad To celebrate World Play Day 2025, I partnered with The  @LEGO Group to create the ultimate LEGO railway adventure #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets! My LEGO train travels through HUGE mountains, glow-in-the-dark and LED lit tunnels and down an insane DIY pool-noodle spiral coaster. But will the train make it or will this end in a complete disaster? 

♡ Get the merch: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (worldwide shipping 🌎)

SUBSCRIBE for a chance at the ecosystem kit
►  https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Meet The Crew!
🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Noodle & Pickle
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry 
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito & Burrito
🦎 Lucy & Lemon
🐠 Peanut & Jelly
🦎 Lime & Pepper & Squeak
🪦 R.I.P. Kirby

Watch as we build an insane 200ft LEGO railway through the studio, passing by some of your favorite animals, including Ralph my Peacock Mantis Shrimp, Mochi, my grocery store lobster, and the beloved duo Lucy and Lemon, my axolotls. We even build my kitten Nori a rube goldberg contraption to feed him treats when the train passes by! In this adventure-filled episode, we also travel to an abandoned railway to learn about trains in the real world! 

This LEGO train trip will have 5 epic stops, including a dual greenhouse filled with live plants and LEGO botanicals, a snowy mountain featuring miniature Christmas trees and LEGO Santa, a cat cafe, a glow-in-the-dark tunnel with glowing crystals and an arid desert ecosystem with LEGO animals and real cacti. The LEGO train will be equipped with a tiny camera so you can see what the train sees, so be on the lookout for all of the hidden LEGO builds along the way! Can you spot them all?

Watch until the end to see if the train makes it through the entire trip in one piece! This video is perfect for anyone who loves LEGO trains, building custom LEGO builds, axolotls, exotic pets, rare animals, DIY projects or is just interested in what it takes to build an epic DIY LEGO railway! 

If you have any comments, suggestions or questions for this LEGO train video or future videos, leave them down in the comments! Also for additional content like this, video tutorials, project sneak peeks and more, follow me on Instagram @aquariuminfo.

If you're reading this, you're a Super Fan!
Comment "Cat Cafe" so I notice you 🐈☕️

Watch as we build an insane 200ft LEGO railway through the studio, passing by some of your favorite animals, including Ralph my Peacock Mantis Shrimp, Mochi, my grocery store lobster, and the beloved duo Lucy and Lemon, my axolotls. We even build my kitten Nori a rube goldberg contraption to feed him treats when the train passes by! In this adventure-filled episode, we also travel to an abandoned railway to learn about trains in the real world! 

This LEGO train trip will have 5 epic stops, including a dual greenhouse filled with live plants and LEGO botanicals, a snowy mountain featuring miniature Christmas trees and LEGO Santa, a cat cafe, a glow-in-the-dark tunnel with glowing crystals and an arid desert ecosystem with LEGO animals and real cacti. The LEGO train will be equipped with a tiny camera so you can see what the train sees, so be on the lookout for all of the hidden LEGO builds along the way! Can you spot them all?

Watch until the end to see if the train makes it through the entire trip in one piece! This video is perfect for anyone who loves LEGO trains, building custom LEGO builds, axolotls, exotic pets, rare animals, DIY projects or is just interested in what it takes to build an epic DIY LEGO railway!

Mein LEGO Zug fährt durch riesige Berge, durch im Dunkeln leuchtende und LED-beleuchtete Tunnel und eine verrückte selbstgebaute Poolnudel-Spiralachterbahn hinunter. ja.title: ペットのために巨大なレゴ鉄道を作りました！
ja.description:
#ad 2025年のワールドプレイデーを記念して、@LEGOグループと提携して究極のレゴ鉄道アドベンチャーを制作しました #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

ペットのために巨大レゴ鉄道を作りました！レゴの列車は、巨大な山々、暗闇で光るLEDライトのトンネル、そしてDIYで作ったプールヌードルのスパイラルコースターを駆け抜けます。果たして列車は無事に到着できるのでしょうか？それとも大惨事に終わるのでしょうか？

♡ グッズはこちら：https://aquariuminfo.com/ (世界中に発送🌎)

エコシステムキットをゲットするチャンス！チャンネル登録はこちら
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

クルーの紹介！
🐈 ノリ
🐲 ギズモ
🦀 ヌードル＆ピクルス
🦞 モチ
🐢 ハリー
🦐 ラルフ
🐸 フリトー＆ブリトー
🦎 ルーシー＆レモン
🐠 ピーナッツ＆ジェリー
🦎 ライム＆ペッパー＆スクイーク
🪦 カービー、安らかに眠れ

スタジオ内を走る全長200フィートのレゴ鉄道を組み立てる様子をご覧ください。お気に入りの動物たちも登場します。私のピーコックシャコのラルフ、スーパーで買ったロブスターのモチ、そして愛しのウーパールーシーとレモン。列車が通る時におやつがもらえる、愛猫のノリのために、ルーブ・ゴールドバーグ風の仕掛けまで作りました！冒険いっぱいのこのエピソードでは、廃線跡にも足を運び、現実世界の列車について学びます！

このレゴ列車の旅には、5つの壮大な停車地点があります。生きた植物とレゴの植物でいっぱいの二重温室、ミニチュアのクリスマスツリーとレゴのサンタが飾られた雪山、猫カフェ、光るクリスタルが輝く暗闇のトンネル、そしてレゴの動物と本物のサボテンが生息する乾燥した砂漠の生態系などです。レゴ列車には小型カメラが搭載されているので、列車が見ているものを見ることができます。道中に隠されたレゴの作品にも注目してください！全部見つけられますか？

列車が無事に全行程を走りきれるか、最後までご覧ください！この動画は、レゴ列車、カスタムレゴ作品の製作、アホロートル、珍しいペット、珍しい動物、DIYプロジェクトが好きな方、あるいは壮大なDIYレゴ鉄道の作り方に興味がある方にぴったりです！

このレゴ列車の動画や今後の動画について、ご意見、ご提案、ご質問がありましたら、コメント欄にお寄せください！このような追加コンテンツ、動画チュートリアル、プロジェクトのプレビューなどについては、Instagram @aquariuminfo をフォローしてください。

これを読んでいるあなたは、私の大ファンです！

snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Trailer
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa, Durgesh Kumar, Sunita Rajwar, Ashok Pathak, Pankaj Jha

A TVF Creation
Created by: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by: Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by: Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey

Official Release Date June 24, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amidst the much-awaited village panchayat elections, Pradhan’s and Bhushan’s camps battle tooth and nail to maintain the upper hand. The future of everyone, including Abhishek, hangs in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: EMOTIONAL INTERVIEW – Behind the scenes of our flooded desert escape
snippet.description:
4WDs RECOVERED AFTER 82 DAYS & emotional interview – Behind the scenes of our flooded desert escape. By now you’ve seen our wild escape from the Simpson Desert floods - but there’s plenty you didn’t see… 🫣

If you did actually miss the eps, check them out here:
Ep 1: https://youtu.be/816Z-XpB0_s
Ep 2: https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

While we were stuck in Birdsville, we sat down with the crew at the Birdsville Pub for a behind-the-scenes chat to spill everything the cameras missed. Grab a beer and tune in! 🍻

ENTREVISTA EMOCIONANTE – Tras bambalinas de nuestra escapada al desierto inundado. Nuestro rescate en la inundación repentina de Capitol Gorge el 23 de junio de 2022. ¡Inundación repentina captada en cámara! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon. 10 inundaciones repentinas devastadoras captadas en cámara. ¡Atrapados en el desierto de Simpson por inundaciones nunca vistas en 50 años! ¿Qué hacemos ahora? ¡Nos estamos quedando sin combustible, comida ni agua en el desierto de Simpson! ¿Lo logramos? 10 días, 1000 km a baja velocidad, ¡pero inundados y atascados! ¿Salimos? ¡Una tormenta que solo ocurre una vez por década inunda la ciudad más seca de Australia! Pero el cruce del río Kimberley inundado salió mal: rápidos de más de 150 m de ancho. ¡Nuestro viaje más épico JAMÁS FILMADO! Pero 5 4x4 se inundaron en Cabo York, ¡y uno fue remolcado a casa! Frenchmans: ¡la inundación más húmeda que jamás hayamos visto! Pero la mayor inundación del lago Eyre en casi 50 años | 7:30, ¡Pero caravanas abandonadas y atrapadas durante una semana en el interior inundado de Australia! ¿Salimos? Pero lo más húmedo que hemos visto en Cape York... Ríos embravecidos y lodo inagotable. Primeros 4x4 en Tele Track 2023 o cualquier otro video como 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media o Mighty Car Mods. Este es un video donde Jock y Jesse se reúnen para una charla reveladora sobre cómo escapar de una inundación del desierto única en la vida.

hi.title: भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - बाढ़ग्रस्त रेगिस्तान से बचने के हमारे सफर के पीछे की कहानी
hi.description:
82 दिनों के बाद 4WDs की रिकवरी और भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - बाढ़ग्रस्त रेगिस्तान से भागने के पीछे की कहानी। अब तक आपने सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान की बाढ़ से हमारे जंगली भागने को देखा होगा - लेकिन बहुत कुछ ऐसा है जो आपने नहीं देखा... 🫣

अगर आपने वाकई एपिसोड मिस कर दिए हैं, तो उन्हें यहाँ देखें:
एप 1: https://youtu.be/816Z-XpB0_s
एप 2: https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

जब हम बर्ड्सविले में फंसे हुए थे, तो हमने बर्ड्सविले पब में क्रू के साथ बैठकर पर्दे के पीछे की बातें कीं और कैमरे से छूटी हुई हर बात बताई। एक बीयर लें और सुनें! 🍻

शॉन, ग्राहम, जॉक और जेसी - जिन्हें पहले 4WD एक्शन के नाम से जाना जाता था - 20+ सालों से ऑस्ट्रेलिया में सबसे बेहतरीन ऑफ-रोड कंटेंट दे रहे हैं। शानदार कार निर्माण और 4x4 टिप्स से लेकर फ्रेजर आइलैंड, यूटा, द किम्बरली, कोलोराडो, द रूबिकॉन ट्रेल और द सिम्पसन डेजर्ट जैसे प्रतिष्ठित स्थानों की खोज तक, हम हर ऑफ-रोडर के लिए कंटेंट बनाते हैं। हमने डोनट मीडिया के दिग्गजों के साथ ट्रैक पर भी धूम मचाई है! चाहे आप पूरी तरह से मॉडिफाइड टोयोटा लैंडक्रूजर चला रहे हों या अपनी हिलक्स या रेंजर के साथ शुरुआत कर रहे हों, हमने आपको 4WD और एडवेंचर से जुड़ी सभी चीज़ों के लिए कवर किया है।

📱 पर्दे के पीछे की सामग्री के लिए हमारे सोशल मीडिया को फॉलो करें
इंस्टाग्राम 👉🏻 @4wd247

भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - हमारे बाढ़ वाले रेगिस्तान से बचने के दृश्यों के पीछे, लेकिन 23 जून 2022 को हमारा कैपिटल गॉर्ज फ्लैश फ्लड रेस्क्यू, लेकिन फ्लैश फ्लड कैमरे पर कैद हो गया! लिटिल वाइल्ड हॉर्स स्लॉट कैन्यन, लेकिन 10 विनाशकारी फ्लैश फ्लड कैमरे पर कैद हो गए, लेकिन 50 साल में नहीं देखी गई बाढ़ से सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान में फंस गए! अब हम क्या करें?, लेकिन सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान में ईंधन, भोजन और पानी खत्म हो रहा है! क्या हम इसे बना पाएंगे? 10 दिन, 1000 किमी कम रेंज में, लेकिन बाढ़ और फंस गए! क्या हम बाहर निकल पाएंगे? दशक में एक बार आने वाले तूफान ने ऑस्ट्रेलिया के सबसे सूखे शहर में बाढ़ ला दी!, लेकिन बाढ़ आ गई किम्बर्ले नदी पार करना गलत हो गया - 150 मीटर से अधिक चौड़ी रैपिड्स - हमारी अब तक की सबसे शानदार यात्रा फिल्माई गई!, लेकिन केप यॉर्क में 5 4WD बाढ़ में डूब गए - 1 को घर ले जाया गया! फ्रांसीसी - हमने इसे अब तक देखा सबसे गीला!, लेकिन लेक आयर में लगभग 50 वर्षों में सबसे बड़ी बाढ़ | 7.30, लेकिन कारवां छोड़ दिए गए और बाढ़ वाले ऑस्ट्रेलियाई आउटबैक में 1 सप्ताह तक फंसे रहे! क्या हम बाहर निकलेंगे?, लेकिन केप यॉर्क में हमने जो सबसे गीला दृश्य देखा है... उफनती नदियाँ और अथाह कीचड़ - टेली ट्रैक 2023 पर पहली 4WD या 4WD 24/7, द ग्रैंड टूर, मैट्स ऑफ़ रोड रिकवरी, डोनट मीडिया या माइटी कार मॉड्स जैसे किसी अन्य वीडियो पर। यह एक ऐसा वीडियो है जिसमें जॉक और जेसी एक बार की रेगिस्तानी बाढ़ से बचने के बारे में ‘सब कुछ बताने’ के लिए बैठते हैं!

ja.title: 感動のインタビュー – 洪水に見舞われた砂漠からの脱出の舞台裏
ja.description:
82日後に4WDが復旧！感動のインタビュー ― 洪水に見舞われた砂漠からの脱出劇の舞台裏。シンプソン砂漠の洪水からのワイルドな脱出劇はご覧いただいたと思いますが、まだ見ていないエピソードもたくさんあります…🫣

もし見逃してしまった方は、こちらからご覧ください。
エピソード1：https://youtu.be/816Z-XpB0_s
エピソード2：https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

バーズビルで足止めされている間、バーズビル・パブのクルーと舞台裏のトークショーを行い、カメラが捉えきれなかったすべてのことを明かしました。ビールを片手に、ぜひご覧ください！🍻

ショーン、グラハム、ジョック、ジェシー（以前は4WD Actionとして活動）は、20年以上にわたりオーストラリアで最高のオフロードコンテンツをお届けしてきました。壮大な車の組み立てや4WDのヒントから、ユタ州のフレーザー島、コロラド州のキンバリー、ルビコントレイル、シンプソン砂漠といった象徴的なスポットの探索まで、あらゆるオフロードライダーのためのコンテンツを制作しています。Donut Mediaのレジェンドたちと一緒にサーキットを走ったこともあります！フル改造されたトヨタ・ランドクルーザーに乗っている方も、ハイラックスやレンジャーに乗り始めたばかりの方も、4WDとアドベンチャーに関するあらゆる情報を網羅しています。

感動インタビュー – 洪水に見舞われた砂漠からの脱出の舞台裏。2022年6月23日、キャピトル・ゴージの洪水救助活動。しかし、洪水の様子はカメラに捉えられていました！リトル・ワイルド・ホース・スロット・キャニオン。10回の壊滅的な洪水がカメラに捉えられていました。しかし、50年ぶりの洪水でシンプソン砂漠に閉じ込められました！さて、どうしよう？, でも、シンプソン砂漠で燃料、食料、水が尽きてしまった！ なんとかたどり着けるかな？ 10日間、低速で1000km走行、でも、洪水と泥沼！ 脱出できるかな？ 10年に一度の嵐がオーストラリアで最も乾燥した町を洪水に襲う！, でも、キンバリー川の横断が失敗に終わり、幅150m以上の急流が流れ込む、これまでで最も壮大な旅になった！, でも、ケープヨークで4WD5台が浸水、1台は自宅まで牽引される！ フレンチマンズ - これまで見た中で最も雨が多い！, でも、エア湖で約50年ぶりの大洪水 | 7.30、でも、キャラバンが放置され、浸水したオーストラリアのアウトバックで1週間足止めされている！脱出できるかな？でも、ケープヨークは今まで見た中で一番の雨…荒れ狂う川と底なしの泥。Tele Track 2023を4WDで初めて下る。あるいは、4WD 24/7、The Grand Tour、Matts Off Road Recovery、Donut Media、Mighty Car Modsなどの動画を参考に。これは、ジョックとジェシーが一生に一度の砂漠の洪水からの脱出について「すべてを語る」動画です！

it.title: INTERVISTA EMOZIONANTE – Dietro le quinte della nostra fuga nel deserto allagato
it.description:
4WD RECUPERATI DOPO 82 GIORNI e intervista emozionante – Dietro le quinte della nostra fuga nel deserto allagato. Ormai avete visto la nostra fuga selvaggia dalle inondazioni del Simpson Desert, ma c'è molto che non avete visto... 🫣

Ep. 2: https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

Shaun, Graham, Jock e Jesse, precedentemente noti come 4WD Action, offrono i migliori contenuti fuoristrada in Australia da oltre 20 anni. Da epiche creazioni di auto e consigli per il fuoristrada all'esplorazione di luoghi iconici come Fraser Island, nello Utah, il Kimberley, in Colorado, il Rubicon Trail e il Simpson Desert, creiamo contenuti per ogni appassionato di fuoristrada. Abbiamo persino percorso le piste con le leggende di Donut Media! Che tu guidi un Toyota Land Cruiser completamente modificato o che tu stia appena iniziando a guidare il tuo Hilux o Ranger, abbiamo tutto ciò che ti serve per il fuoristrada e l'avventura.

INTERVISTA EMOZIONANTE – Dietro le quinte della nostra fuga nel deserto allagato, ma il nostro salvataggio dall'alluvione improvvisa di Capitol Gorge del 23 giugno 2022, ma l'alluvione improvvisa è stata ripresa dalle telecamere! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon, ma 10 alluvioni improvvise devastanti sono state riprese dalle telecamere, ma INTRAPPOLATI NEL DESERTO DEI SIMPSON DA UN'ALLUVIONE mai vista da 50 anni! Cosa facciamo ora?, Ma stiamo finendo carburante, cibo e acqua nel deserto di Simpson! Ce la faremo? 10 giorni, 1000 km a basso regime, Ma ALLAGATI E IMPANATI! Ne usciremo? Una tempesta che una volta ogni decennio allaga la città PIÙ ASCIUTTA d'Australia!, Ma L'attraversamento del fiume Kimberley ALLAGATO È ANDATO STORTO - rapide larghe oltre 150 m - il nostro viaggio più epico MAI FILMATO!, Ma 5 fuoristrada ALLAGATI A CAPE YORK - 1 viene trainato a casa! Frenchmans - la PIÙ PIOVOSA che abbiamo mai visto!, Ma La più grande alluvione del lago Eyre in quasi 50 anni | 7.30, Ma ROULOTTE ABBANDONATE e bloccate per 1 settimana nell'outback australiano allagato! Usciamo? Ma il CAPE YORK PIÙ PIOVOSO CHE ABBIAMO MAI VISTO... fiumi impetuosi e fango senza fondo - i primi fuoristrada sul Tele Track 2023 o qualsiasi altro video come 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media o Mighty Car Mods. Questo è un video in cui Jock e Jesse si siedono per una chiacchierata "raccontata" sulla loro fuga da un'alluvione nel deserto, un evento irripetibile!

4x4 RÉCUPÉRÉS APRÈS 82 JOURS & interview émouvante – Dans les coulisses de notre évasion dans le désert inondé. Vous avez déjà vu notre évasion sauvage des inondations du désert de Simpson, mais il y a plein de choses que vous n'avez pas vues… 🫣

Shaun, Graham, Jock et Jesse – anciennement connus sous le nom de 4WD Action – proposent le meilleur contenu tout-terrain d'Australie depuis plus de 20 ans. Des constructions automobiles épiques aux conseils 4x4, en passant par l'exploration de lieux emblématiques comme Fraser Island (Utah), le Kimberley (Colorado), le Rubicon Trail et le désert de Simpson, nous créons du contenu pour tous les passionnés de tout-terrain. INTERVIEW ÉMOTIONNELLE – Dans les coulisses de notre évasion dans le désert inondé. Notre sauvetage lors de l'inondation soudaine de Capitol Gorge le 23 juin 2022 : une inondation soudaine filmée ! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon : 10 inondations soudaines dévastatrices filmées. Piégés dans le désert de Simpson par des inondations inédites depuis 50 ans ! Que faire maintenant ? À court de carburant, de nourriture et d'eau dans le désert de Simpson ! Allons-nous y arriver ? 10 jours, 1 000 km en gamme basse, mais INONDÉS ET ENROULÉS ! On s'en sort ? Une tempête, une fois par décennie, inonde la ville la plus SÈCHE d'Australie !, mais la traversée de la rivière Kimberley INONDÉE a mal tourné – des rapides de plus de 150 m de large – notre voyage le plus épique JAMAIS FILMÉ !, mais 5 4x4 INONDÉS À CAPE YORK – l'un d'eux est remorqué jusqu'à chez lui ! Frenchmans – le PLUS HUMIDE que nous ayons jamais vu !, mais la plus grande inondation du lac Eyre depuis près de 50 ans | 7h30, mais des CARAVANES ABANDONNÉES et coincées pendant 1 semaine dans l'Outback australien inondé ! On s'en sort ? Mais CAPE YORK, c'est LE PLUS MOUILLÉ QU'ON AIE VU... Rivières déchaînées et boue sans fond - Premiers 4x4 sur Tele Track 2023 ou toute autre vidéo comme 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media ou Mighty Car Mods. Voici une vidéo où Jock et Jesse discutent de leur évasion d'une inondation désertique unique !

EMOTIONALES INTERVIEW – Hinter den Kulissen unserer Flucht aus der überfluteten Wüste. Unsere Sturzflutrettung in der Capitol Gorge am 23. Juni 2022. Die Sturzflut wurde gefilmt! Der Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon. Zehn verheerende Sturzfluten wurden gefilmt. In der Simpson-Wüste eingeschlossen – eine Flut, wie sie seit 50 Jahren nicht mehr zu sehen war! Was tun wir jetzt? In der Simpson-Wüste gehen uns Sprit, Essen und Wasser aus! Schaffen wir es? 10 Tage, 1000 km im niedrigen Gang, aber ÜBERSCHWEMMT und SITZEND! Kommen wir da raus? Ein Sturm, der alle zehn Jahre vorkommt, überschwemmt Australiens TROCKENSTE Stadt!, Aber die ÜBERSCHWEMMTE Kimberley-Flussüberquerung ist SCHIEFGEGANGEN – über 150 m breite Stromschnellen – unsere spektakulärste Reise, die je gefilmt wurde!, Aber 5 Geländewagen IN CAPE YORK ÜBERSCHWEMMT – 1 wird nach Hause geschleppt! Frenchmans – das NASSESTE, was wir je gesehen haben!, Aber die größte Überschwemmung des Lake Eyre seit fast 50 Jahren | 7.30, Aber WOHNWAGEN VERLASSEN und säßen 1 Woche lang im überschwemmten australischen Outback fest! Kommen wir raus? Aber DAS NASSESTE, DAS WIR IN CAPE YORK GESEHEN HABEN ... TOSENDE Flüsse und bodenloser Schlamm – die ersten Allradfahrzeuge auf dem Tele Track 2023 oder in anderen Videos wie 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media oder Mighty Car Mods. Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon, Namun 10 Banjir Bandang yang Menghancurkan Tertangkap Kamera, Namun TERPERANGKAP DI GURUN SIMPSON OLEH BANJIR yang tidak terlihat dalam 50 tahun! Apa yang harus kami lakukan sekarang?, Namun Kehabisan bahan bakar, makanan & air di Gurun Simpson! Apakah kita berhasil? 10 hari, 1000 km di daerah rendah, Tapi TERBANJIRI & TERJEBAK! Apakah kita bisa keluar? Badai yang terjadi sekali dalam satu dekade Membanjiri kota TERKERING di Australia!, Tapi penyeberangan sungai Kimberley yang TERBANJIRI BERAKHIR – jeram selebar 150 m+ - perjalanan paling epik yang PERNAH DIFILMKAN!, Tapi 5 kendaraan roda empat TERBANJIRI DI CAPE YORK - 1 berhasil diderek pulang! Orang Prancis - yang TERBASAH yang pernah kami lihat!, Tapi banjir terbesar di Danau Eyre dalam hampir 50 tahun | 7.30, Tapi KARAVAN DITINGGALKAN & terjebak selama 1 minggu di pedalaman Australia yang banjir! Apakah kita akan keluar?, Tapi YANG PALING BASAH YANG PERNAH KITA LIHAT DI CAPE YORK... ENTREVISTA EMOCIONANTE – Nos bastidores da nossa fuga pelo deserto alagado. Mas o nosso resgate por inundação repentina na Capitol Gorge em 23 de junho de 2022, mas a inundação repentina foi registrada! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon, mas 10 inundações repentinas devastadoras foram registradas, mas PRESOS NO DESERTO DE SIMPSON POR INUNDAÇÕES não vistas há 50 anos! O que fazemos agora?, Mas Ficar sem combustível, comida e água no Deserto de Simpson! Conseguiremos? 10 dias, 1000km em baixa velocidade, Mas INUNDADO E ATOLADO! Conseguiremos sair? Uma tempestade que ocorre uma vez a cada década inunda a cidade MAIS SECA da Austrália!, Mas INUNDADA a travessia do rio Kimberley DEU ERRADO – corredeiras com mais de 150m de largura - nossa viagem mais épica JÁ FILMADA!, Mas 5 4x4 INUNDADOS EM CABO YORK - 1 é rebocado para casa! Frenchmans - o MAIS CHUVOSO que já vimos!, Mas A maior enchente do Lago Eyre em quase 50 anos | 7h30, Mas CARAVANAS ABANDONADAS e presas por 1 semana no Outback australiano inundado! Vamos sair? Mas o Cabo York mais chuvoso que já vimos... Rios caudalosos e lama sem fundo - primeiros 4x4 na Tele Track 2023 ou qualquer outro vídeo como 4x4 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media ou Mighty Car Mods serviria. snippet.title: Los Angeles protests against ICE immigration raids continue; U.S. Marines, National Guard deployed
snippet.description:
More National Guard troops and hundreds of Marines have been deployed to Los Angeles as violent protests continued for another night, with more than 100 arrests Monday.

California Gov. Gavin Newsom continued to denounce sending the military into the city, filing an emergency motion to block the Marines' deployment. The National Guard has been protecting a federal complex in LA where some immigrants are being held after ICE raids around the city.

hi.title: वीजीजी संग्रहालय प्रगति! मेरे जॉन डीयर के साथ एक बाड़ और पेड़ हटा रहा हूँ!
hi.description:
अब समय आ गया है कि इमारत के पिछले हिस्से को साफ किया जाए, ताकि ज़्यादा जगह मिल सके और निर्माण की तैयारी की जा सके। किसी को पैसे देने के बजाय, एक व्यक्ति अपनी जॉन डीयर कार लेकर शहर में चला गया, ताकि देख सके कि वह क्या साफ कर सकता है!

https://www.vicegripgarage.com

fr-FR.title: PROGRÈS AU MUSÉE VGG ! Abattage d'une clôture et d'arbres avec mon John Deere !

Consultez notre autre chaîne YouTube :
https://www.youtube.com/c/vicegripgarage

Découvrez nos produits dérivés sur :
https://www.vicegripgarage.com

Visita nuestro otro canal de YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/c/vicegripgarage

Puedes encontrar productos en:
https://www.vicegripgarage.com

it.title: VGG PROGRESSI AL MUSEO! Rimozione di una recinzione e di alberi con il mio John Deere!

snippet.title: I Tried To Make Something In America (The Smarter Scrubber Experiment) - Smarter Every Day 308
snippet.description:
Get a Smarter Scrubber Here: http://smarterscrubber.com
Interested in Wholesale, or helping us tell the story? Here's a link:
https://forms.gle/XFrLTa5b8kxSvPnu8

I would like to thank the Patrons of Smarter Every Day. They knew about this project early and helped make it happen.
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

John is a great Dad and a good dude. Check out JJGeorge here:
https://www.jjgeorgestore.com/

Our goal is to make these things 100% in America. We're going to have to build some machines in order to do this.
Your support is appreciated.

Mantle's 3D Printing for injection molds is a technology I'm very excited to explore. 
A huge thanks to Ted for participating!
Here's a video on what they do: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uywWr6-nHF4

A HUGE thanks to our Injection Molder Chris Robson, with tons of work from Jeremy:
http://www.robsonco.com/

T&C Metal Stamping (Ask to speak to Weston and tell him Destin sent you!)
https://www.tandcstamping.com/

Search Engine Podcast: 
Episode "The Puzzle of the All-American BBQ Scrubber"
https://www.searchengine.show/the-puzzle-of-the-all-american-bbq-scrubber/

Check out Jeremy Fielding's Channel
https://www.youtube.com/@Jeremy_Fielding

Check out Tim Cook's comments on China at the Fortune Global Forum:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ng8xQ-SNGc

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GET SMARTER SECTION

I recommend learning about the Bretton Woods Accords
https://www.federalreservehistory.org/essays/bretton-woods-created

Read about the Bretton Woods system
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bretton_Woods_system

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Smarter Every Day on Patreon
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

Ambiance, audio and musicy things by: Gordon McGladdery 
https://www.ashellinthepit.com/
http://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/

Warm Regards,

Destin

snippet.title: Apple WWDC 2025 keynote in 28 minutes

Apple just wrapped WWDC 2025 and packed a bunch of major updates into its annual Worldwide Developer Conference keynote. Some of the major announcements include: new “Liquid Glass” design coming to all systems, new windowing capabilities to iPadOS 26, Messages will get custom backgrounds and new group chat features like Polls. snippet.title: Four Days Later - Is the Switch 2 REALLY Worth $450?
snippet.description:
The Nintendo Switch 2 launched June 5, and now that the initial excitement and hype has died down, its time to review the unit. The Switch 2 represents an upgrade to the original Switch from 2017, but is it worth the $450 of your hard earned money? Lets dive in and take a closer look at the hardware.

TimeStamps:

00:00 - Intro
01:31 - Screen Brightness vs Switch OLED
02:36 - Setting up
03:10 - MicroSD Express and Game Key Cards
04:37 - Mario Kart World
06:11 - Fast Fusion & Cyberpunk 2077
08:23 - Back Compat with Switch 1
09:35 - Switch 2 Edition Updates
10:54 - Gamechat
13:10 - GameCube and N64 NSO
14:40 - Wi-Fi Speed Tests

LYRICS:
 
You said your phone was broken
Just forgot to charge it
Whole outfit you’re wearing
God I hope it’s ironic
Did you just say you’re finished?
Didn’t know we started
It’s all just so familiar
Baby, what do you call it?
Stupid
Or is it
Slow?
Maybe it’s
Useless?
But there’s a cuter word for it
I know
Manchild
Why you always come a running to me?
Fuck my life
Won’t you let an innocent woman be?
Never heard of self care
Half your brain just aint there
Manchild
Why you always come a running
Taking all my loving from me?
Why so sexy
If so dumb?
And how survive the earth so long?
If I’m not there it won’t get done
I choose to blame your mom
Manchild
Why you always come a running to me?
Fuck my life
Won’t you let an innocent woman be?
Never heard of self care
Half your brain just aint there
Manchild
Why you always come a running
Taking all my loving from me?
Oh I like my boys playing hard to get
And I like my men all incompetent
And I swear they choose me
I’m not choosing them
Amen
Hey men!
Oh, I like my boys playing hard to get
And I like my men all incompetent
And I swear they choose me
I’m not choosing them
Amen
(Amen)
Hey men!
(Hey men!)
Manchild
Why you always come a running to me?
(always come a running to me)
Fuck my life
Won’t you let an innocent woman be?
Oh, I like my boys playing hard to get
And I like my men all incompetent
And I swear they choose me
I’m not choosing them
Amen
Hey men!
 
#SabrinaCarpenter #Manchild

snippet.title: 3 Days Solo Survival On A Deserted Island (No Food, No Water, No Fire)
snippet.description:
FDYS SHOP 🔥 GET YOUR MERCH  https://www.fielddaysshop.com  

In this epic survival challenge, I'm stranded on a deserted island with no food, no water, and no fire! Can I survive for 3 whole days using only my wits and basic skills? Watch as I navigate the harsh tropical environment, search for shelter, and try to find ways to quench my thirst and hunger. From building a makeshift shelter to finding creative sources of sustenance, I'll show you how to stay alive on a deserted island with minimal resources. Don't miss this thrilling adventure and find out if I can make it out alive!

FDYS SHOP 🔥 GET YOUR MERCH  https://www.fielddaysshop.com  

FIELD DAYS INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/field__days 

MAKY AND MATT - YOUTUBE  https://www.youtube.com/@MakyandMatt 

FIELD DAYS IN SPANISH  https://www.youtube.com/@fielddaysenespanol 

OTIS SUNNIES 🕶️ https://au.otiseyewear.com/?ref=MATTF...

EP 218

snippet.title: Velcro Suit Mini Games w/Pierson! - Camp CrunchLabs Week 1
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first week of Camp CrunchLabs! This week the nephews return to challenge their favorite uncle! It's not too late to join Camp CrunchLabs! Join here: http://www.campcrunchlabs.com 

Check out Disney's Elio, only in theaters June 20: https://movies.disney.com/elio
#Elio

Each build-it-yourself STEM toy teaches the magic and fun in engineering principles and coincides with exclusive weekly videos like this one that accelerate your learning! Ready for Camp? Visit http://www.campcrunchlabs.com for  more info.

A big thanks to our special guest @pierson for joining me on mercury!

This weeks Challenge:
CREATE SOMETHING AWESOME USING FORCED PERSPECTIVE!
Just like my buddy Zach King or all the photos you see of people at the Leaning Tower of Pisa, use forced perspective to create something awesome!!! Maybe you are driving a shoe as a car, scaling a mountain that is really the floor or creating huge items from household items the sky is the limit!

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR CHALLENGES?
Parents: Tag challenge project video submissions @crunchlabs with #CampCrunchlabsContest on Instagram, X, TikTok or Facebook. Then complete this form https://www.crunchlabs.com/pages/camp-planet-page-mercury
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Contest begins at 9:00 a.m. PT on 6/7/25 & ends 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/23/25; but, to be eligible to win Grand Prize, one must enter by 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/8/25. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., who are 18+ and the parent or legal guardian of at least (1) child between 8-16 years of age. Grand Prize winner must travel 7/20/25-7/22/25. See Official Rules for full details including entry periods, entry requirements, prize descriptions and judging criteria. Void where prohibited.
Full rules: http://crunchlabs.com/camp-rules

It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. snippet.title: Roland-Garros 2025 - Coco Gauff, French Open winner : "I feel like I'm on top of the world"
snippet.description:
#rolandgarros #frenchopen #rg25 #grandslam #grandchelem #tennis #Gauff #Sabalenka #WTA 

Coco Gauff tient enfin son premier titre à Roland-Garros. La numéro 2 mondiale est allée au bout d'elle-même, samedi, sur la terre battue du Court Philippe-Chatrier. Malgré une manche de retard à face la numéro 1 mondiale Aryna Sabalenka, l'Américaine de 21 ans a gardé le cap et élevé son niveau de jeu pour recoller au score et même renverser la vapeur. Bien aidée, certes, par les 70 fautes directes de la Biélorusse, la Floridienne est allée chercher sa victoire, son deuxième titre du Grand Chelem après l'US Open 2023, et son premier à Roland-Garros, trois ans après sa finale perdue contre Iga Swiatek. Fait amusant, Gauff avait rêvé en 2021 qu'elle remporterait Roland-Garros 2025... Dingue.

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

localized.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
localized.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

snippet.title: Wicked: For Good | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The epic conclusion comes to theaters this November. Watch the #WickedForGood trailer now  🧹🫧

Pre-save ‘Wicked: For Good – The Soundtrack’ at https://wickedthesoundtrack.com
-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@wickedmovie
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wickedmovie
X: https://twitter.com/wickedmovie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wickedmovie
Official Site: https://wickedmovie.com

And now whatever way our stories end, I know you have rewritten mine by being my friend …

Last year’s global cinematic cultural sensation, which became the most successful Broadway film adaptation of all time, now reaches its epic, electrifying, emotional conclusion in Wicked: For Good. 

Directed once again by award-winning director Jon M. Chu and starring the spectacular returning cast, led by Academy Award® nominated superstars Cynthia Erivo and Ariana Grande, the final chapter of the untold story of the witches of Oz begins with Elphaba and Glinda estranged and living with the consequences of their choices. 

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), now demonized as The Wicked Witch of the West, lives in exile, hidden within the Ozian forest while continuing her fight for the freedom of Oz’s silenced Animals and desperately trying to expose the truth she knows about The Wizard (Jeff Goldblum).  

Glinda, meanwhile, has become the glamorous symbol of Goodness for all of Oz, living at the palace in Emerald City and reveling in the perks of fame and popularity. Under the instruction of Madame Morrible (Oscar® winner Michelle Yeoh), Glinda is deployed to serve as an effervescent comfort to Oz, reassuring the masses that all is well under the rule of The Wizard.  

As Glinda’s stardom expands and she prepares to marry Prince Fiyero (Olivier award winner and Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey) in a spectacular Ozian wedding, she is haunted by her separation from Elphaba. She attempts to broker a conciliation between Elphaba and The Wizard, but those efforts will fail, driving Elphaba and Glinda only further apart. The aftershocks will transform Boq (Tony nominee Ethan Slater) and Fiyero forever, and threaten the safety of Elphaba’s sister, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), when a girl from Kansas comes crashing into all their lives. 

As an angry mob rises against the Wicked Witch, Glinda and Elphaba will need to come together one final time. With their singular friendship now the fulcrum of their futures, they will need to truly see each other, with honesty and empathy, if they are to change themselves, and all of Oz, for good. 

Wicked: For Good also stars Emmy nominee Bowen Yang and Bronwyn James as Glinda’s fawning assistants, Pfannee and ShenShen and BAFTA and Grammy nominee Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, or Change) as the voice of Elphaba’s childhood nanny, Dulcibear. 

The film is produced by returning Tony and Emmy winning powerhouse Marc Platt p.g.a. and by multiple Tony winner David Stone. The executive producers are Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman and Dana Fox. The first film, Wicked, released in November 2024, earned 10 Academy Award® nominations, including Best Picture, and won the Oscars® for Costume Design and Production Design. To date, the film has grossed $750 million worldwide. 

Wicked: For Good is based on the generation-defining musical stage play with music and lyrics by legendary Grammy and Oscar® winning composer and lyricist Stephen Schwartz and book by Winnie Holzman, from the bestselling novel by Gregory Maguire. The screenplay is by Winnie Holzman and Winnie Holzman & Dana Fox. The film score is by John Powell & Stephen Schwartz, with music and lyrics by Stephen Schwartz.

snippet.title: Amerie: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
This Black Music Month, Tiny Desk honors the anniversaries of landmark albums that have shaped the course of music and culture.

Alanté Serene | June 6, 2025
When Amerie arrived at the Tiny Desk, her enthusiastic energy and bright smile was an instant mood boost. The warm entrance felt fitting for an artist whose music embodies the soul of summer: bold percussion, breezy vocals and the feeling of endless possibilities.

When her sophomore album Touch dropped in 2005, it introduced a national audience to the infectious rhythms of go-go. Rooted in Washington, D.C., go-go is known for its layered percussion, funky basslines and live instrumentation made to hype the crowd. These sounds pulse through Amerie's music and helped to make "1 Thing" a standout in a year overflowing with R&B hits.

Amerie, who once lived in Washington, D.C. for several years, returns to the city with a reimagined set accompanied by go-go legends Backyard Band. Together, they open the show with songs from her debut album All I Have, including "Talkin' to Me" and the quintessential summer anthem "Why Don't We Fall in Love." She eases into her latest single, "Mine," and delivers a fan-favorite "I Just Died," before introducing a new rendition of "Rolling Down My Face" that you'll want to hear all the time from now on. By the time "Talkin' About" kicks in, Amerie is in full dance mode. When "1 Thing" closes out the set, she steps from behind the Desk to join the dance party, turning the performance into a celebration.

SET LIST
"Talkin' to Me"
"Why Don't We Fall in Love"
"Mine"
"I Just Died"
"Rolling Down My Face"
"Talkin' About"
"1 Thing"

MUSICIANS
Amerie: vocals
Warren Jones: keys 
Michael Dunklin: keys
Eric Britt: keys
Bobby Terry: guitar
Eugene Chapman: alto saxophone
Nathaniel Fields: bass
Paul Edwards: drums
Keith Robinson: percussion
Tanesia Mack: background vocals
Tonaee' Burgess: background vocals
Zay'Marie: background vocals

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Alanté Serene
Director/Editor: Maia Stern
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Host/Series Producer: Bobby Carter
Videographers: Maia Stern, Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Elizabeth Gillis
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistants: Dora Levite, Ashley Pointer
Photographer: Grace Raver
Tiny Desk Series Editor: Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

#nprmusic #tinydesk #amerie

snippet.title: #4 PACERS at #1 THUNDER | NBA FINALS GAME 1 HIGHLIGHTS | June 5, 2025
snippet.description:
The Pacers defeated the Thunder, 111-110 tonight in Oklahoma City. Pascal Siakam led the way for the Pacers with 19 points on 7-15 from the field (1-2 from 3) to go along with 10 rebounds and 3 assists. For the Thunder, Shai Gilgeous-Alexander had a team-high 38 points on 14-30 from the field (3-6 from 3). The Pacers lead the series 1-0.

The Indiana Pacers mounted an incredible comeback in the 4th quarter, at one point down 15 points, they managed to rally back and in the end it was Tyrese Haliburton who once again put the team ahead late! This is the FIFTH time this postseason that the Pacers have rallied from a 15+ point deficit, which is the MOST by any team in the playoffs since 1998! They also have become just the third team in NBA Playoffs history to rally from a 15 point deficit in the 4th quarter, joining the 2011 Dallas Mavericks and the 1992 Chicago Bulls. Haliburton's shot to put the team ahead with 0.3 seconds remaining put Tyrese in the history books, as that marks the FIFTH time this playoff run where he has made a go-ahead, game-winning or game-tying shot within the last 30 seconds of the 4th quarter or in overtime, the most of ANY player in NBA Playoff history! The record was formerly held by Ray Allen in his 2009 run, with four made shots of that variety.

snippet.title: Trump-Musk row explodes as billionaire claims President named in Epstein files | BBC News
snippet.description:
The political partnership between Donald Trump and Elon Musk has exploded  in spectacular fashion into a bitter war of words.

It began when Mr Trump said he was “surprised and disappointed” at Elon Musk’s criticism of his flagship spending bill.   He said they had had a “great relationship” but “I don’t know if we will any more”. 

Elon Musk responded on his social media platform X with a series of increasingly heated remarks about his former boss.   He said the President’s claims that he has supported the budget bill were “false”.   He said Mr Trump was  “ungrateful” for his help in getting elected and would have lost the election without his financial support.   Mr Musk warned that the President’s tariffs policy would lead to a recession.

Then Musk made an explosive allegation, claiming without evidence that Donald Trump is named in the files about the late convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein.  He said that “is the real reason they have not been made public”.

Donald Trump suggested that the easiest way to save money would be to terminate the billions of dollars in government contracts and subsidies that go to Elon Musk’s companies.   Musk said that President Trump should be impeached.

Reeta Chakrabarti presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Sarah Smith and Simon Jack.

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news 

#BBCNews

ja.title: 非常に危険な嵐が襲来しようとしています...
ja.description:
今日の天気予報では、今後数日間、アメリカに厳しい天候をもたらす巨大な嵐についてお伝えしています。強風、大きな雹、竜巻の脅威などが予想されます。さらに、活発な気象パターンが定着するため、6月中旬まで厳しい天候が続くと予想されています。今日の天気予報で最新情報をご確認ください。
